        damage: -{floor(lastCounterRequestedAmount*0.5)}[heal]
  - type: text
    text: When you take damage of the chosen type, you can use your reaction to gain immunity against that instance of the damage, and you regain a number of hit points equal to half the damage you would have taken. Once this reaction is used, it can't be used again until the next dawn.
    title: Damage Absorption
_v: 2
proper: true
verb: uses their
list_display_override: 'Uses absorbing tattoo, use `-amt #` to signify how much damage you are absorbing'"""

